<figureCitation box="[1101,1172,829,853]" captionStart="Figs" captionStartId="20.[136,180,1309,1331]" captionTargetBox="[137,1476,189,1295]" captionTargetId="figure-378@20.[133,1484,181,1303]" captionTargetPageId="20" captionText="Figs. 80–90. Morphological features of Metrocoris species. 80–83: M. ciliatus, macropterous male. 80: right fore leg. 81, 82: left paramere, two different views. 83: endosomal sclerites, lateral view. 84, 85: M. inthanon. 84: right fore leg of male. 85: apex of abdomen, female, ventral view. 86–90: M. triangulatus. 86–89: male holotype. 86: A, right fore leg. 87: left paramere. 88, 89: endosomal sclerites, lateral and dorsal views. 90: abdomen of female, ventral view (80, 84, 86 same scale; 81–83 same scale; 85, 90 same scale)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4502656" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4502656/files/figure.png" pageId="19" pageNumber="128">81, 82</figureCitation>
